{"tid":782522,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女係咪雞?","createTime":"2018-08-16T20:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T21:03:12.000Z","uid":152224,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbb7e32c5bd87b3024b5b5cad522c64f4d15e41","tid":782522,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:42:48.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<br />\n<br />\n我同條女係由細玩到大嘅朋友 <br />\n因為住得近,雙方父母係fd (公屋仔女）<br />\n我同佢都係A0<br />\n大家都互當彼此係朋友<br />\n單獨出街數目數之不盡<br />\n<br />\n其實我偷偷暗戀住佢（但佢只當我係最好嘅朋友）<br />\n我幫佢渡過好多難關<br />\n我諗住等我事業有成（考到政府工）<br />\n就同佢表白...<br />\n<br />\n點知今日佢同我講佢出pool了<br />\n而且只係同條仔約會咗一次（有d太隨便?)<br />\n佢地喺交友app識嘅<br />\n條仔條件極好（但有可能造假?)<br />\n自稱: 中大medic（IB狗）,身高185,住私樓,精通多樣運動樂器, IQ 145<br />\n<br />\n但條女同我講過自己唔拜金 <br />\n願意同對方一齊捱供樓<br />\n但如今只係同對方出咗一次街就拍拖 <br />\n末免令人感覺佢只係一個為錢而活的臭雞而已...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47644ca4a785d5e486050555a047d543e044163e","tid":782522,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:45:01.000Z","msg":"同呢個朋友拍咗五年拖？"},{"pid":"d807db9eb3e099b6f23d524d89ac81a16172e49f","tid":782522,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:45:58.000Z","msg":"冇睇篇文 係"},{"pid":"0e3f89a2f3458bf50b79a542e0547d2bb0787c68","tid":782522,"uid":138981,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:46:15.000Z","msg":"喺連登乜女都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝唔到女又話人雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做暑期功課啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfcb1729797d1c05a4fab16228980b3847577a5","tid":782522,"uid":138981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:48:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌你老母死假膠</span></span></strong><br />\nA0呀哪<br />\n浪費晒啲巴絲同你嘥時間傾足咁多頁<br />\n<br />\n拍咗5年拖嘅女朋友比醫科生溝咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.k